x4freetext: DESCRIPTION OF THE EXPERIMENTAL ARRANGEMENT.

x4codes.hlp: Universita degli Studi di Torino + INFN Torino, Italy

x4freetext: THE DOSE OF IRRADIATION FOR TARGET WAS 2960 ROENTGEN.
CYLINDRICAL TARGET OF BI-209.
. TYPE L4, THICKNESS = 400 MU.
THE BACKGROUND WAS NEGLIGIBLE.
STATISTICAL ERRORS ARE PRESENTED.
. EXPERIMENTAL SPECTRA ARE COMPARED WITH THE
EVAPORATION THEORY. A CONTRIBUTION OF HIGH ENERGY
NEUTRONS OUTSIDE THE EVAPORATIVE CURVE DIVIDED BY
THE TOTAL NEUTRON NUMBER OVER E=2 MEV IS REPORTED.
THE CONTRIBUTION OF THE PHOTONEUTRONS ARISING FROM
THE BI(GAMMA,2N) PROCESS IS EVALUATED.
PHOTONEUTRON SPECTRUM FROM BI SHOWS AROUND 90 DEGREES
A SUPRISINGLY HIGH CONTRIBUTION OF NEUTRONS OUTSIDE
THE CALCULATED EVAPORATIVE SPECTRUM.
. DATA WERE COMPILED IN SCJAD OF SARATOV STATE
UNIVERSITY.
CORRECTED BY V.VARLAMOV, V.MCLANE
